title: Stocks to Watch: The Global Energy Outlook
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin speaks with deputy editor Ben Levisohn and Jonathan Waghorn, portfolio manager of Guinness Atkinson Asset Management on the outlook for global energy markets.
